<span class="quote1">&gt;ダメでしょうか？</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt;</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt;update item set  itenname = itemname +  &quot;予備&quot;   WHERE `code` =1234</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt;</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt;文字列に予備が付きません。</span>
